## Multi-Tenant: Missing business_id Filter
**Severity**: 🔴 Critical
**Symptom**: User A sees User B's data
**Cause**: Query forgot `.eq('business_id', businessId)`
**Fix**: Always filter by business_id in every query
**Prevention**: Use a wrapper function `getScopedQuery(table, businessId)` that enforces it

## RLS Policy Not Applied
**Severity**: 🔴 Critical
**Symptom**: Data visible across tenants despite policy
**Cause**: Forgot `ALTER TABLE x ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;`
**Fix**: Enable RLS on every new table
**Prevention**: db-migrator agent checks this automatically

## RTL: margin-left Breaks in Hebrew
**Severity**: 🟠 High
**Symptom**: Spacing looks wrong in Hebrew UI
**Cause**: Hardcoded `ml-*` instead of logical `ms-*`
**Fix**: Use `ms-*`, `me-*`, `ps-*`, `pe-*` instead
**Prevention**: rtl-checker agent catches this

## Green API Rate Limits
**Severity**: 🟠 High
**Symptom**: Messages fail silently after burst
**Cause**: Green API has per-minute rate limits
**Fix**: Use Upstash Redis queue with throttling
**Prevention**: Always send through queue, never direct

## Stripe Webhook Signature Verification
**Severity**: 🔴 Critical
**Symptom**: Webhooks accepted from anyone
**Cause**: Missing `stripe.webhooks.constructEvent` signature check
**Fix**: Always verify webhook signatures in API route
**Prevention**: security-auditor agent flags this

## Supabase Edge Function Timeout
**Severity**: 🟡 Medium
**Symptom**: Function fails after 10 seconds
**Cause**: Edge Function max execution time
**Fix**: Move long operations to background job or queue
**Prevention**: Keep Edge Functions under 5 seconds

## Hebrew Font Not Loading
**Severity**: 🟡 Medium
**Symptom**: Hebrew text renders in fallback font
**Cause**: Font file not loaded or wrong font-family
**Fix**: Load Assistant/Heebo/Rubik from Google Fonts or self-host
**Prevention**: Test RTL rendering during component review

